OL,3,CMan charged with murder over death of
OL,4,Cgrandfather in suspected carjacking
OL,6,FPolice investigating the death of a
OL,7,Fman who is thought to have been run
OL,8,Fover by his own car have charged a man
OL,9,Fwith murder.
OL,11,FChristopher Hanley, 57, died on
OL,12,FOlympic Street in Beswick in Greater
OL,13,FManchester on Saturday 16th March.
OL,15,FHe was pronounced dead at the scene
OL,16,Fdespite the best efforts of emergency
OL,17,Fservices.
OL,19,FMarvin Sutton, 35, of no fixed abode
OL,20,Fhas now been charged with murder.
