OL,4,Cgrandfather in suspected carjacking
OL,6,FPolice say he's been remanded into
OL,7,Fcustody ahead of an appearance at
OL,8,FTameside Magistrates on Tuesday.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, a 43-year-old man remains
OL,11,Fon bail on suspicion of assisting an
OL,12,Foffender.
OL,14,FChris's family paid this tribute to
OL,15,Fhim on Monday: "As a family we are
OL,16,Fheartbroken and shocked at the sudden
OL,17,Floss of Chris.
OL,19,F"A loved and devoted family man who
OL,20,Fadored his grandchildren, tragically
OL,21,Fand unfairly, taken way too soon.
